Package com.adobe.creativesdk.typekit

Contains classes for adding Typekit font support.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AdobeTypekitFont.ITypekitCallback<T,ET>
    Interface used to indicate the result of an operation related to Typekit Font.
    AdobeTypekitFontFamily.ITypekitCallback<T,ET>
    Interface used to indicate the result of an operation related to Typekit Font Family.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdobeTypekitFont
    AdobeTypekitFont is the class through which user handles operations with Typekit fonts.
    AdobeTypekitFont.FontFilePath
    The class provides the details of the font file.
    AdobeTypekitFontBrowser
    AdobeTypekitFontBrowser is the class through which user interacts with Font Browser component.
    AdobeTypekitFontFamily
    Represents a Typekit font family.
    AdobeTypekitManager
    Manages download of Typekit fonts and related information.
    TypekitNotification
    Indicates a Typekit notification.
    TypekitNotification.Event
    Represents several events generated in response to Typekit operations.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AdobeTypekitException.ErrorCode
    The Typekit Error Codes.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AdobeTypekitException
    Indicates a Typekit Exception.
    UserNotAuthenticatedException
    Indicates that the user has not been authenticated to access the Typekit service.
